//www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>已故说唱老将<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fatman-scoop">法特曼·斯库普</a>的死因已经揭晓。</p><p>这位说唱歌手的真名是艾萨克·弗里曼 (Isaac Freeman)， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rap-icon-fatman-scoop-has-died-after-suffering-medical-emergency-on-stage-3789417">上个月末（8 月 30 日）在康涅狄格州表演时在舞台上晕倒后去世</a>。他今年 56 岁。</p><p>倒塌后，市长劳伦·加勒特在社交媒体上证实，弗里曼正被救护车送往医院。这位说唱歌手的巡演经理 DJ Pure Cold 后来在 Instagram 上发帖证实弗里曼已经去世。 </p><figure id="attachment_3789782" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3789782" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3789782" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270.jpg" alt="胖子勺。照片来源：Naomi Rahim/WireImage" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3789782" class="wp-caption-text">胖子勺。照片来源：Naomi Rahim/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>现在，在<a href="https://apnews.com/article/fatman-scoop-dead-heart-disease-d2df783c70779d9dcb9555440ba56fdd" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>美联社</em></a>的一份新报道中，康涅狄格州法医办公室证实法特曼·斯库普死于心脏病。这位说唱歌手还患有高血压和动脉粥样硬化性心血管疾病，这是一种由动脉壁斑块堆积引起的心脏病。</p><p>在他去世的消息传出后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/missy-elliott-questlove-nicki-minaj-lead-tributes-to-fatman-scoop-truly-one-of-the-best-voices-in-hip-hop-3789732">几位